Type: Package
Package: tidyfilter
Title: Filter Profanity From Text
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Mark McPherson [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Mark McPherson <mark.mcpherson1@nhs.net>
Description: Fast profanity filtering using a trie data structure. Also exports
  a filter_words function that can be used in a dplyr pipeline.
